## STRICT RULES

### Design system

- Use **Tailwind utilities** from **`tailwind.config.js`** (`text-ink-*`, `px-gutter`, `bg-gradient-primary`, `text-footer-*`, …). Do not scatter raw hex in HTML—extend the theme if a value is missing (`docs/design-system.md`).
- **No inline styles** except third-party embeds if unavoidable.
- **Semantic class grouping** in markup: layout → spacing → typography → color → border → shadow → state.

### Colors (token → hex)

- **Primary gradient (CTA):** `#9c6cfe` → `#5000ea` (single brand gradient only).
- **Accent (text emphasis / eyebrow):** `#5f15ee` (`brand-600`).
- **Ink:** `#0f1117` (950), `#212325` (900), `#2a2d36` (800), `#2d3148` (850), `#5e6472` (700 FAQ answer), body `#1e1e1e`.
- **Surfaces:** page `#fefeff`, white `#ffffff`, lilac `#f9f6ff` / `#f0ebff`, FAQ pill `#f5f0ff` (`lilac-25`).
- **Borders:** `#e2e4eb` (`border-border-subtle`), `#efefef`, `#d9d9d9`, lilac `#e0d5ff`.
- **Footer (Home MCP):** background `#0f1117`; column labels `#c4aaff` (**JetBrains Mono**); body links `rgba(255,255,255,0.7)`; tagline `0.55` opacity; legal `0.4` / `0.5` tiers.

### Typography

- **Logo:** Aeonik Medium (or licensed substitute) ~`23px` for wordmark.
- **UI / marketing:** Satoshi Regular / Medium / Bold.
- **Eyebrows / FAQ pill:** TT Firs in Figma → `font-display` + `text-faq-badge` or `text-eyebrow` + `text-brand-600` per context.
- **Footer column titles:** `font-mono text-eyebrow-mono text-footer-label uppercase`.
- **Hero H1:** `text-display-home` / `text-display-verify`.
- **Section H2:** `text-heading-2` (Verify-style **50px** lh) or `text-heading-faq` for FAQ block (**44px** / **44px**).
- **Body:** `text-body-lg`; FAQ answers `text-body-faq text-ink-700`.

### Spacing

- **Mobile section:** `py-10`; **desktop:** `lg:py-section-y` (**60px**); **footer:** `lg:py-section-y-footer` (**74px**).
- **Container:** `max-w-content mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-gutter`.
- **Gaps:** CTA row `14–20px`; nav links `28px`; grids `gap-8` default for 4-up cards.

### Radius

- **Primary pill:** `rounded-pill` on `h-14`; **secondary hero pill:** `rounded-pill-secondary` (**42px**); **cards:** `rounded-card`; **ghost CTAs:** `rounded-pill-soft`.

### Shadows

- **Card / chip / primary:** use `shadow-card`, `shadow-chip`, `shadow-primary` utilities from config.

### Button system

- **Primary:** gradient + white bold text + `h-14` + `shadow-primary` + icon `16px` optional.
- **Secondary:** white + `border-border-subtle` + `text-ink-950` + `h-14` + `rounded-pill-secondary`.
- **Ghost outline CTA:** `h-btn-ghost px-btn-ghost-x rounded-pill-soft border-border-subtle` (e.g. “Choose your path”, “Contact our team”).
- **Hover:** subtle brightness or `translate-y-0.5`—pick one project-wide (`animation-rules.mdc`).

### Icons

- **Lucide only**, `stroke-width` **1.5**, sizes **`16px`** (buttons), **`14px`** (inline “learn more” chevrons), **`20px`** (checklist rows).

### Gradients

- **CTA / primary actions:** `9c6cfe → 5000ea` only.
- **Ambient hero blobs:** very low opacity purple blends—optional; never behind small text.

### Animations

- Prefer **CSS** transitions; **transform + opacity** only; `duration-md` / `duration-slow`; easing **`ease-premium`**.
- See `docs/animation-system.md`.

### Component rules

- Sections = reusable partials; IDs from `docs/page-architecture.md`.
- No duplicated 15+ class chains—promote to config `@layer components` or theme shortcuts.

### Code quality

- Mobile-first, accessible landmarks, lazy images, meaningful `alt`, minimal DOM depth.

## DO NOT

- Use random purples outside the documented system.
- Mix icon libraries.
- Use Bootstrap or heavy UI kits.
- Add decorative motion to stars/lines/grids.
